("A Fun, Fast-Paced Game", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant offers fun and fast-paced gameplay, but the character balance could use some work. The matches are exciting, and it's a great option for people who love shooters.", 4.00, 288, 22),
("Good Concept, Needs More Polishing", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant has great potential, but it feels a bit unpolished. The gameplay is fun, but there are still bugs that detract from the experience. Hopefully, these issues are addressed in future updates.", 3.50, 288, 30),
("A Good Shooter", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant is a solid shooter with great mechanics. The variety of characters adds depth, but the game can feel a bit unbalanced at times. It's still fun and worth playing if you enjoy team-based games.", 4.00, 288, 38),
("Entertaining, but Needs Work", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant is fun to play, but it has some balancing issues and a few technical problems. The core gameplay is exciting, but the game needs a little more polish to reach its full potential.", 3.50, 288, 46),
("Exciting but Unfinished", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant has a lot of exciting potential, but it still feels unfinished. The gameplay is fun, but the lack of balance and stability issues hold it back from being great.", 3.50, 288, 54),
("Great FPS Action", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "The FPS action in XDefiant is fantastic. The fast-paced gameplay keeps you on your toes, but the game still needs work in terms of balancing and bug fixing.", 4.00, 288, 62),
("Fun, but Needs Balance", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant is a fun game, but it feels a little imbalanced at times. The different characters are great, but some of them need better balancing to make the game more fair for everyone.", 3.50, 288, 70),
("A Promising Shooter", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant has a lot of promise, but it still has a few rough edges. The gameplay is solid, but balancing and bugs are an issue. I'm excited to see where this game goes in the future.", 4.00, 288, 78),
("Fun, but Needs Polish", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "XDefiant offers fast and exciting gameplay, but it needs more work. The game is fun, but it's held back by balancing issues and occasional bugs.", 3.50, 288, 86),
("A Masterpiece of Storytelling", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is an incredible RPG with a gripping story, expansive world, and deep characters. The combat is fun and engaging, and it's easily one of the best RPGs of its generation.", 5.00, 32, 10),
("Immersive and Engaging", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "The world of Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is beautifully crafted, and the story keeps you hooked from start to finish. The combat is fluid and strategic, making it an unforgettable experience.", 4.50, 32, 18),
("Epic Journey", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 delivers an epic adventure with amazing character development and an emotionally charged story. The combat is complex, but rewarding. A must-play for RPG fans.", 5.00, 32, 26),
("Incredible World and Story", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 has one of the most immersive worlds I've ever experienced in an RPG. The storyline is captivating, and the battles are well-designed. Highly recommend!", 4.50, 32, 34),
("A Truly Stunning RPG", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "The gameplay in Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is fantastic, and the narrative is so engaging. There's a lot to explore, and the game constantly surprises you with its depth and charm.", 5.00, 32, 42),
("Deep and Emotional", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 combines a deep narrative with a fantastic battle system. The world is beautifully designed, and the music is memorable. The characters are well-written, and the story is emotional.", 4.50, 32, 50),
("A Truly Special Game", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is a special game. The story is amazing, the combat is deep, and the characters are unforgettable. It's a game that truly makes you feel something.", 5.00, 32, 58),
("Masterpiece of Design", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is a design masterpiece. The vast world and the intricate combat system make it an incredibly satisfying RPG. The characters and story are top-tier as well.", 4.50, 32, 66),
("Fantastic RPG Experience", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 is one of the best RPGs I've ever played. The game offers an emotional and thrilling journey, with plenty of memorable characters and epic battles.", 5.00, 32, 74),
("An RPG Like No Other", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Xenoblade Chronicles 3 sets a new standard for RPGs. It's got an amazing world, brilliant combat, and a story that really pulls you in. It's an unforgettable experience.", 4.50, 32, 82),
("A New Beginning for the Yakuza Series", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon takes the series in a new direction with a turn-based combat system and a fresh protagonist. It's still got the heart of the series, but with a more modern twist.", 4.00, 52, 11),
("A Fresh Take on Yakuza", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon introduces new mechanics that breathe new life into the series. The story is engaging, the characters are memorable, and the turn-based combat is a refreshing change.", 4.50, 52, 19),
("A Fantastic New Direction", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon is a fantastic new entry in the series. The new turn-based combat system is a fun twist, and Ichiban is a great new protagonist. The side stories are as crazy and fun as ever.", 4.50, 52, 27),
("Fresh and Entertaining", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon takes the series in a new direction, but it keeps the quirky side missions and interesting characters that make the Yakuza series so unique. It's a refreshing change.", 4.00, 52, 35),
("Yakuza Like Never Before", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon is a great addition to the series. The new combat system works really well, and Ichiban is a fantastic character. The story is engaging, and the side activities are as entertaining as ever.", 4.50, 52, 43),
("A New Chapter", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon introduces a new combat system that works surprisingly well. Ichiban is a likable lead, and the story is packed with both heart and humor. The side content is also a blast.", 4.50, 52, 51),
("A Reinvented Classic", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon is a reinvented classic. The new turn-based combat system fits perfectly with the series, and Ichiban is a welcome addition. The game retains the humor and charm that made the series so beloved.", 4.50, 52, 59),
("A Perfect Balance of Drama and Comedy", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon strikes a perfect balance between serious moments and absurd humor. The turn-based combat adds a new layer of strategy, and the story is emotional and heartfelt.", 4.50, 52, 67),
("A Bold Move", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon is a bold move for the series. The new protagonist and combat system are a great change, but the game still has all the wild side content you love. Definitely worth playing!", 4.00, 52, 75),
("Yakuza at Its Best", "2025-01-18 11:04:58", "Yakuza: Like a Dragon is one of the best in the series. The new combat system is fun and strategic, and Ichiban is a character I immediately connected with. The side content is quirky and fun, as always.", 4.50, 52, 83);
